WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.300
Your conspiracy has been exposed

2
00:00:01.300 --> 00:00:03.000
It's no use getting angry here

3
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:04.266
See clearly

4
00:00:04.266 --> 00:00:06.766
Father has decided to break off the father-son relationship with you

5
00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:08.900
If you get down on your knees now and kowtow three times

6
00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:10.000
Confess to your father

7
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:10.800
And then...

8
00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:13.466
Sign this divorce agreement

9
00:00:13.466 --> 00:00:16.300
We can consider letting you live

10
00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:18.666
Impossible. My son would never hurt anyone

11
00:00:18.666 --> 00:00:20.300
You must be mistaken.

12
00:00:20.733 --> 00:00:21.900
Kowtow and tremble

13
00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:23.400
sever ties

14
00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:25.500
Is this what Dad means or what you mean?

15
00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:27.100
What difference does it make?

16
00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:29.766
Even if you stay in the Jiang family shamelessly now

17
00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:31.366
You won't get a penny.

18
00:00:31.366 --> 00:00:34.300
It's better for Zhijun to get out of here

19
00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:39.100
I never wanted your Jiang family's money

20
00:00:39.100 --> 00:00:40.666
My dad and I have thicker blood than water

21
00:00:40.666 --> 00:00:42.533
If Dad really thinks I did this to him

22
00:00:42.533 --> 00:00:43.966
If you want to cut ties with me

23
00:00:43.966 --> 00:00:45.800
Then let Dad come and tell me in person

24
00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:47.800
Otherwise I would never sign

25
00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:49.400
It's a toast

26
00:00:49.400 --> 00:00:51.800
Then go ahead and take it all apart for me

27
00:00:52.100 --> 00:00:52.733
No.

28
00:00:52.733 --> 00:00:55.366
This is the only place where Xiao Cai can live

29
00:00:55.366 --> 00:00:56.500
You can't take it apart?

30
00:00:56.500 --> 00:00:58.966
I'm going to make you homeless.

31
00:00:58.966 --> 00:01:00.566
No place in Pingcheng

32
00:01:00.566 --> 00:01:01.500
Do it!

33
00:01:13.666 --> 00:01:15.766
You... you've gone too far.

34
00:01:15.766 --> 00:01:17.900
How is that okay?

35
00:01:17.900 --> 00:01:19.466
You want us to stop?

36
00:01:19.466 --> 00:01:20.966
I'll give you a chance.

37
00:01:20.966 --> 00:01:23.533
As long as you can prove that you donated the bone yourself

38
00:01:23.533 --> 00:01:24.500
Dad saved by marrow

39
00:01:24.500 --> 00:01:26.733
I can not only leave you this stinky house

40
00:01:26.733 --> 00:01:29.700
Only then can the whole river be delivered to you

41
00:01:29.700 --> 00:01:31.133
Care about your property in Jiangjiang

42
00:01:31.133 --> 00:01:33.700
I just want you to get on your knees and kowtow to my mom and apologize

43
00:01:33.700 --> 00:01:34.966
Then get out

